          <td style=3D"padding-bottom: 36px; color: #000000; font-size: 16p=
x; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;">It=E2=80=99s intere=
sting to compare Anderson=E2=80=99s arc with Herm=C3=A8s=E2=80=99s <b>Nad=
=C3=A8ge Vanh=C3=A9e</b>, who also recently celebrated a decade in the hot =
seat and is a designer to watch in this never-ending game of musical chairs=
=2E They are two very different hous=
es, with different challenges=E2=80=94Loe=
we had no position when Anderson started, Herm=C3=A8s is forever the hegemo=
n=E2=80=94but it=E2=80=99s still impressive to see how zippy Vanh=C3=A9e ha=
s made Herm=C3=A8s feel. There was an athleticism to this collection: lots =
of cropped shirts and tank tops, and the bodies she chose to display them o=
n were athletic, too. I loved the boxy practicality of the top-handle Plume=
, the choice for those who already own <i>every</i> other bag. <br/><br/>Pr=
acticality was the name of the game at McQueen, too. What I liked about thi=
s collection was the tailoring. We=E2=80=99re seeing a lot of twisted waist=
s this
season, and <b>Se=C3=A1n McGirr</b>=E2=80=99s jackets cut a fine silhouette=
=2E I also thought the staging, with th=
e models walking down a runway reminis=
cent of a foggy, haunting lagoon, was effective. But I=E2=80=99d like to se=
e something more daring, too. It=E2=80=99s tough to be as inexperienced <i>=
and </i>scrutinized as McGirr. By comparison, I always think about <b>Raf S=
imons</b>=E2=80=99 first 10 years in business=E2=80=94he had all that time =
to develop his themes before landing at Jil Sander. <br/><br/>Perhaps McGir=
r has the constitution to handle it all, and I imagine the Kering brass are=
 happy to let him take his time, given that they have far bigger fish to fr=
y. (<b>Fran=C3=A7ois-Henri Pinault </b>and his deputy, <b>Francesca Bellett=
ini</b>, frankly looked <i>relaxed</i> in the front row at McQueen as Pinau=
lt=E2=80=99s wife, <b>Salma Hayek</b>, snapped photos on her phone.) But fa=
shion is always hungry for a phenomenon, and that=E2=80=99s simply not what=
 this is. If McGirr succeeds in the end, it=E2=80=99s going to be a
